          <title>Right-hander Nick Pivetta, Padres finalize $55M four-year contract</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Right-hander Nick Pivetta and the San Diego Padres officially announced a finalized $55 million, four-year contract on Monday, a backloaded deal that allows him to opt out after the 2026 and '27 seasons.]]></description>
