          <title>Yankees' Stanton hasn't swung bat in 3 or 4 weeks and is unsure of whether he can play in opener</title>
          <description><![CDATA[New York Yankees slugger Giancarlo Stanton hasn’t swung a bat in three or four weeks and isn’t sure whether he will be ready for opening day because of painful tendinitis in both elbows.]]></description>
