        <item>
          <title>William Byron avoids late wrecks to win 2nd straight Daytona 500</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Ninth in the No. 24 Chevrolet with one lap left, Byron was in the right place by racing near the outside wall in overtime to became the first back-to-back winner since Denny Hamlin in 2019-20.]]></description>
