          <title>Measure for county to back ban on trans women in sports fails</title>
          <description><![CDATA[An effort to get San Diego County to throw its support behind a bill in Congress that would ban transgender girls and women from competing in women's sports failed when it was brought forward at the Board of Supervisors on Tuesday.]]></description>
